>"},{"pid":"bdb14e16d2f37389018aa01009010bacb66ee927","tid":1737320,"uid":270905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"勇武靜靜地贏係必要既<br />\n但我地同時要keep住make noise. 除左三罷同開花都要諗諗其他"},{"pid":"9da40836585048a7a8a71623733b966bd78a0bf0","tid":1737320,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbf3ba8855189ce54aae79cee1af9a6114ca43a","tid":1737320,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"正常post 無人推"},{"pid":"57568e06695c1b8fdf018cf69e1fb32f0f8d40a0","tid":1737320,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbbf3ba8855189ce54aae79cee1af9a6114ca43a","tid":1737320,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:47:02.000Z","msg":"正常post 無人推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"是但  衰過就會識改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗三個月唔好打陣地戰終於有人提要地下化<br />\n可能過多三個月就知分曉  到底係靜定唔靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ed7bf4cd296aa0b3dda9cee90e4685b779330e","tid":1737320,"uid":18043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"6b66774968eddaa46903d9c6bf0042999e09638c","tid":1737320,"uid":18043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33d403657c32aeb19c5b253780eebf19d681b3fb","tid":1737320,"uid":228049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:01:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f4430af1ea28959598cbfeb79bf5ff2102bc7af","tid":1737320,"uid":209679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae76f0f7835af26696af33601d02068f58e3f64b","tid":1737320,"uid":343546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過靜雞雞靜靜雞贏可能都係一個風向？？？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1783379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1783379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}